  "3010060": {
    "name": "DEATH PLUNDER-亡命掠夺者",
    "steam_appid": 3010060,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >定制你的角色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的角色背景，选择你的天赋，分配属性点，构筑你的角色优势，是百步穿杨的神射手，还是力大无穷的大力士，或是迅捷如风的偷袭者，一切都由你自己决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/505a17c23cdb0f1cb33dc91f137227e8.poster.avif?t=1772376386\" width=608 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/505a17c23cdb0f1cb33dc91f137227e8.webm?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/505a17c23cdb0f1cb33dc91f137227e8.mp4?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武装你的角色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的装备的系统，每件装备都有视觉上的变化，并有着不同的部位防护效果，请做好防护，迎接僵尸们致命的攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/7d004fb5ed688ecdc8e52e54d0c7e026.poster.avif?t=1772376386\" width=608 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/7d004fb5ed688ecdc8e52e54d0c7e026.webm?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/7d004fb5ed688ecdc8e52e54d0c7e026.mp4?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >改装你的武器：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有多种基础枪械与近战武器，可以进行改装与保养你的武器，优秀的掠夺者要时常保养维护自己的武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/9a8a8af226b46143ec76a6566159d793.poster.avif?t=1772376386\" width=608 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/9a8a8af226b46143ec76a6566159d793.webm?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/9a8a8af226b46143ec76a6566159d793.mp4?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >种类多样的丧尸：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从普通的丧尸到特殊着装的丧尸再到变异体，不同的丧尸拥有不同的能力，有的数量众多，有的迅捷如风，有的坚若磐石，有的异常致命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/0f99734a4f0122124445e707e79d5c28.poster.avif?t=1772376386\" width=608 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/0f99734a4f0122124445e707e79d5c28.webm?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/0f99734a4f0122124445e707e79d5c28.mp4?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索充满危险的禁区：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >民宅，公寓，警察局，超市，不同的场景会有不同的物资分布，并蕴含着一些秘密，根据需求规划你的行动路线，并安全的撤离。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/02860206f497394692fb37a499ffc274.poster.avif?t=1772376386\" width=608 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/02860206f497394692fb37a499ffc274.webm?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/02860206f497394692fb37a499ffc274.mp4?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经营你的基地：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜集物资扩建升级你的营地，建造工作台，种植箱，捕猎场，净水器等设施，获取生存必需品。制作各种工具，帮助你在这危险的小岛上生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新的战斗演示：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/823827e3e5fcef33e254ced9b2fb8423.poster.avif?t=1772376386\" width=540 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/823827e3e5fcef33e254ced9b2fb8423.webm?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/823827e3e5fcef33e254ced9b2fb8423.mp4?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/1aba2e6cf706c1c47a688308f9042ff8.poster.avif?t=1772376386\" width=540 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/1aba2e6cf706c1c47a688308f9042ff8.webm?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/1aba2e6cf706c1c47a688308f9042ff8.mp4?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/7007670302ca9b15e9177ffe5109662c.poster.avif?t=1772376386\" width=540 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/7007670302ca9b15e9177ffe5109662c.webm?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/7007670302ca9b15e9177ffe5109662c.mp4?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >天气系统演示：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/ce72cf4122bb3cb15cfb7bc55340364b.poster.avif?t=1772376386\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/ce72cf4122bb3cb15cfb7bc55340364b.webm?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/ce72cf4122bb3cb15cfb7bc55340364b.mp4?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >满月&amp;雨夜：因为满月的月光相对明亮，视野相对清晰的常规天气，偶尔也会下雨或者暴雨。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/f7cb6541cb034d3d7f8c30efdd6be6a4.poster.avif?t=1772376386\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/f7cb6541cb034d3d7f8c30efdd6be6a4.webm?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/f7cb6541cb034d3d7f8c30efdd6be6a4.mp4?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >月蚀：因为月光被遮蔽，整个区域被伸手不见五指的黑夜笼罩，如果不依靠灯光将会什么都看不见，你不知道夜幕里到底隐藏着什么危险！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/174736ffac1c270edf6af7dd6c524708.poster.avif?t=1772376386\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/174736ffac1c270edf6af7dd6c524708.webm?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010060/extras/174736ffac1c270edf6af7dd6c524708.mp4?t=1772376386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >血月&amp;血雨：血红的满月把整个世界染成了地狱般的血色，有时还会下起血雨，在血月的影响下所有丧尸都会变的更加嗜血，移动速度变快，伤害更高，千万小心，在血月出门是非常危险的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于反馈与建议：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏目前处于开发阶段，我们计划中还有一些功能与内容没有开发完成，团队目前只有2个人，我们大概需要2年左右的时间来完成正式版的开发，请给予我们反馈与帮助，让我们一起来完成正式版的开发，关于更多抢先体验的问题，请阅读版头的“抢先体验游戏”说明，感谢各位的支持。</p>",
